絲打facebook club呢啲最鍾意cap新聞圖就post上去 搞到蘋果立場冇哂錢賺<br />\n<br />\n［慶祝夠未］警 世 文！一齊打返起文宣戰線好嗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1890283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1890283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1e5648e2b441744d0cd1dd79115eb813e236b448","tid":1892621,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd602b6341ed9f43d45da56701550c9d397fe95d","tid":1892621,"uid":30788,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"香港無可能得咁少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"你意思係個數係假？"},{"pid":"cf7d97184805f60d2c86facb914a339b022c01cd","tid":1892621,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fde67dc0c050f2dea4204cf0c03919030b5f13e8","tid":1892621,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"聽日就過比你睇<br />\n香港跌出前六"},{"pid":"5118d881bdc57fd6bf890d96baabca03ba5b9443","tid":1892621,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:45:25.000Z","msg":"多謝支那解決全球人口老化問題"},{"pid":"3bf4d16b25323cc05e8ff1c950c332a270170f0e","tid":1892621,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:47:26.000Z","msg":"伊朗都追緊"},{"pid":"71ddb57b190427e2f08a6ea4d17034ae6fa710e5","tid":1892621,"uid":271807,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"cd602b6341ed9f43d45da56701550c9d397fe95d","tid":1892621,"uid":30788,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"香港無可能得咁少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:49:15.000Z","msg":"因為香港市民警覺性高，數日間就幾乎全民口罩，呢隻數群聚傳播好勁，又有無病症已經可否傳播，戴口罩係會有效減慢傳播速度"},{"pid":"489eee4f2c7488ff3187667537dd2f42d12066ba","tid":1892621,"uid":45821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e5648e2b441744d0cd1dd79115eb813e236b448","tid":1892621,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd602b6341ed9f43d45da56701550c9d397fe95d","tid":1892621,"uid